e progress indicator\">Genuine progress indicator</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Performance_indicator\" title=\"Performance indicator\">Performance indicator</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/SA8000\" title=\"SA8000\">SA8000</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Social_return_on_investment\" title=\"Social return on investment\">Social return on investment</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Whole-life_cost\" title=\"Whole-life cost\">Whole-life cost</a></li></ul>\n</div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\" class=\"navbox-group\" style=\"width:1%\"><a href=\"/wiki/Environmental_accounting\" title=\"Environmental accounting\">Environmental<br />accounting</a></th><td class=\"navbox-list navbox-odd\" style=\"text-align:left;border-left-width:2px;border-left-style:solid;width:100%;padding:0px\"><div style=\"padding:0em 0.25em\">\n<ul><li><a href=\"/wiki/Carbon_accounting\" title=\"Carbon accounting\">Carbon accounting</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Eco-Management_and_Audit_Scheme\" title=\"Eco-Management and Audit Scheme\">Eco-Management and Audit Scheme</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Emission_inventory\" title=\"Emission inventory\">Emission inventory</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Environmental_full-cost_accounting\" title=\"Environmental full-cost accounting\">Environmental full-cost accounting</a>&#160;/&#32;<a href=\"/wiki/Environmental_impact_assessment\" title=\"Environmental impact assessment\">impact assessment</a>&#160;/&#32;<a href=\"/wiki/Environmental_management_system\" title=\"Environmental management system\">management system</a>&#160;/&#32;<a href=\"/wiki/Environmental_profit_and_loss_account\" title=\"Environmental profit and loss account\">profit-and-loss account</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/ISO_14000\" title=\"ISO 14000\">ISO 14000</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/ISO_14031\" title=\"ISO 14031\">ISO 14031</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Life-cycle_assessment\" title=\"Life-cycle assessment\">Life-cycle assessment</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Pollutant_release_and_transfer_regi